			<CASNumber>1344-28-1</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">White Fused Alumina, a processed and high-purity form of aluminum oxide, is manufactured through the fusion of calcined alumina in electric arc furnaces at high temperatures, followed by a cooling process. It is characterized by its high hardness and chemical inertness, making it suitable for refractories and abrasives. The product is compliant with industry standards, and is utilized predominantly in surface finishing, grinding, and cutting applications. The information further details the production route from bauxite, the educt name 'alumina', and its distribution either to consumers or direct availability at the production plant.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">白色熔融氧化铝是一种经过处理且纯度较高的氧化铝形式，通过在电弧炉中对煅烧氧化铝进行高温熔融之后的冷却过程而制成。其具有高硬度和化学惰性的特点，适用于耐火材料和磨料。产品符合行业标准，并主要用于表面精加工、研磨和切割应用。信息进一步详述了从铝土矿到氧化铝（产品流的原材料名称）的生产路线，以及产品向消费者的分配或在生产工厂的直接可用性。</common:generalComment>
